WEBVTT

00:00.606 --> 00:01.873
<i>Previously on "Heartland":</i>

00:01.940 --> 00:04.341
But we can be friends.
I mean we are friends, right?

00:04.409 --> 00:06.844
Just... we can be
more than that.

00:06.912 --> 00:08.746
Jack Bartlett,
nice to see you again.

00:08.814 --> 00:09.881
He's a good guy,

00:09.948 --> 00:11.382
and he's not just
an oil guy.

00:11.449 --> 00:12.549
It's gonna take me
some time

00:12.617 --> 00:14.585
to get used to you
dating the enemy.

00:14.653 --> 00:16.687
