by money, mom.

00:16.755 --> 00:17.453
Especially Caleb.

00:17.521 --> 00:19.589
Oh, then why did it take him
less than 10 seconds

00:19.657 --> 00:21.258
to accept
my sponsorship money?

00:21.325 --> 00:23.359
You paid him
to go away?

00:23.427 --> 00:24.494
What's this?

00:24.561 --> 00:26.196
It's a little somethin'
to help you out.

00:26.264 --> 00:28.564
Should be enough to tide you over
for a year or so.

00:28.632 --> 00:29.532
<i>She's a great girl, right?</i>

00:29.600 --> 00:30.834
<i>She sure is.</i>

00:30.902 --> 00:32.902
If you hurt her,
I'll have to kill you.

00:32.969 --> 00:33.869
You know that,
right?

00:33.937 --> 00:35.437
So what do you wanna do?

00:35.505 --> 00:37.606
I've actually, uh,
been talking to Scott.

00:37.674 --> 00:39.675
- Really?
- I could hang out with him,

00:39.742 --> 00:42.444
or... you know,
intern, apprentice.

00:42.512 --> 00:43.612
Well,
that's pretty awesome.

00:43.680 --> 00:44.847
There's somethin'
I gotta tell you.

00:44.915 --> 00:46.615
Well, I have something
I wanna tell you, too.

00:48.084 --> 00:50.618
Get the hell outta here!
Leave!

00:52.087 --> 00:53.521
More tests?

00:53.588 --> 00:55.756
Wednesday, next week,
8 am.

00:55.825 --> 00:57.192
I'll be there.

00:57.259 --> 00:58.226
Just say it.

01:00.595 --> 01:01.529
I love you.

