02:04.956 --> 02:06.223
- Who?
- Who do you think?

02:06.591 --> 02:07.591
Peter.

02:07.659 --> 02:09.193
Well, he's in Dubai.

02:09.261 --> 02:10.894
What, they don't have phones
in Dubai, now?

