for dinner with someone else.

02:21.672 --> 02:23.172
Oh, a little bit insecure,
are we?

02:23.240 --> 02:24.207
Easy for you to say!

02:24.275 --> 02:25.308
Your guy's
a stone's throw away.

02:25.376 --> 02:27.610
Mm-hm. I know,
and I love it!

02:27.677 --> 02:29.011
Okay. Bye.

02:35.752 --> 02:37.553
Hello?

02:37.621 --> 02:40.088
Yep, he's here.
Hang on.

02:40.990 --> 02:42.290
It's Lisa!

02:43.492 --> 02:44.826
Hey there!

02:44.894 --> 02:47.094
Welcome back, stranger.

02:47.162 --> 02:48.797
When did your flight
get in?

02:53.769 --> 02:54.803
Hey!

02:54.870 --> 02:56.604
- Hello!
- Good morning!

02:56.672 --> 02:58.371
I wish I could
just skip school.

02:58.440 --> 02:59.205
It's only
a few more weeks.

02:59.273 --> 03:00.273
I know!

03:00.341 --> 03:02.743
Then lots of time
to spend together.

03:02.811 --> 03:04.711
- You should really, um, go...
- What?

03:04.779 --> 03:05.913
- To school.
- Mmm...'Kay!

03:07.348 --> 03:08.381
Ow!

03:09.451 --> 03:10.751
I am gonna miss my bus!

03:10.819 --> 03:11.819
Goodbye!

03:14.855 --> 03:15.655
<i>Hey!</i>

03:16.690 --> 03:19.291
You're not gonna miss it.

03:21.227 --> 03:22.595
- On?
- Yup.

03:27.300 --> 03:28.200
Bye!

03:28.268 --> 03:28.968
Have a good day!

03:34.707 --> 03:36.475
<i>You guys are unbelievable!</i>

03:36.542 --> 03:37.976
- What?
- Oh, come on!

03:38.043 --> 03:39.978
It took you how long
to get together?

03:40.045 --> 03:40.812
Yeah, and now
you're inseparable!

03:40.880 --> 03:43.014
Uh, yeah.
It's totally vomit-inducing.

03:43.082 --> 03:44.215
Oh, thanks.
Harsh.

03:44.283 --> 03:45.649
Well, it is!

03:45.717 --> 03:47.451
True love.
Keep it.

03:47.519 --> 03:49.119
You're such a cynic!

03:49.187 --> 03:50.387
Like I wouldn't be?

